Title: A Woman's Life
Writer: Stéphane Brizé (scenario), Florence Vignon (scenario), Guy de Maupassant (novel)
Actors: Judith Chemla, Jean-Pierre Darroussin, Yolande Moreau, Swann Arlaud
Plot: A fragmented account of the life of Jeanne as she sets out on the path of adult life and gradually experiences the harsh realities of a woman's life in the 19th-century.
